{* *! version 1.1.1  02mar2015}{...}
    {cmd:acosh(}{it:x}{cmd:)}
{p2colset 8 22 22 2}{...}
{p2col: 描述：} {it:x} 的反双曲余弦,{break}
        {cmd:acosh(}{it:x}{cmd:)} =
        ln{{it:x}+sqrt({it:x}*{it:x} - 1)}{p_end}
{p2col: 定义域：} 1 到 8.9e+307 {p_end}
{p2col: 值域：} 0 到 709.77 {p_end}
{p2colreset}{...}